title: SHA-GUILTY PLEA + RHOBH Sutton Sit-Down Recap
itunes:title: SHA-GUILTY PLEA + RHOBH Sutton Sit-Down Recap
description:
Lots happening in the Housewives universe---Jen Shah of RHOSLC changes her plea to guilty, plus Danny recaps this week's episode of The Real Housewives of Beverly Hills, which featured more excuses from Kyle, Rinna forcing a cater waiter to touch her feet, and a Diana and Sutton sit-down.
